<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to <%= shoppieName %></title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff758c 0%, #ff7eb3 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 300;
      }
      .header .emoji {
        font-size: 48px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        display: block;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #ff758c;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .features {
        background: #fff6f8;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .features h3 {
        color: #ff758c;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .features ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .features li {
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: block;
        width: 200px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff758c 0%, #ff7eb3 100%);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }
      .cta-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      .help-section {
        background: #fffbe6;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffcc00;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }
      .social-links {
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .social-links a {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 10px;
        color: #ff758c;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <span class="emoji">🛍️</span>
        <h1>Welcome to <%= shoppieName %></h1>
        <p>Your online shopping experience starts here!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="greeting">Hi <%= name %>! 👋</div>

        <p>
          We're so excited to have you join <strong><%= storeName %></strong>!
          Your account has been created with the email:
          <strong><%= email %></strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="features">
          <h3>🛒 What you can do now:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>🔐 Securely log in to your account</li>
            <li>🧺 Browse trending and best-selling products</li>
            <li>💳 Add to cart and make seamless purchases</li>
            <li>📦 Track your orders in real-time</li>
            <li>🎁 Enjoy exclusive member-only deals and discounts</li>
            <li>📝 Manage your profile and preferences easily</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="cta-button">Shop Now</a>

        <div class="help-section">
          <h3>🆘 Need Help?</h3>
          <p>
            Our support team is ready to help with anything—from order issues to
            product questions.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Contact us:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <p>
          Thanks for being part of our shopping community. We’re here to make
          your shopping smooth, fun, and rewarding.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px">
          With appreciation,<br />
          <strong>The <%= storeName %> Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">Instagram</a> |
          <a href="#">Twitter</a> |
          <a href="#">TikTok</a>
        </div>
        <p>
          This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't create an account
          with us, please let us know.
        </p>
        <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= shoppieName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>🛍️ Making shopping fun, fast, and fabulous.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
